  introLines:
  - Fascinating! The dust patterns on your scales indicate you had a turkey sandwich
    for lunch at exactly 12:15
  - The case of my sudden demise is elementary! Though, admittedly, slightly embarrassing
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I was tracking a highly suspicious character who stole
    a local bakery's prized sourdough starter. I staked out the kitchen, hid inside
    the commercial freezer unit, and the latch accidentally clicked shut from the
    outside
  answerWhatKindOfLife: Brilliant, observational, and completely dedicated to solving
    the neighborhood's smallest mysteries without ever asking for a single penny
    in return
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I am a master consultant of deduction! I find lost house
    keys, track down missing alley cats, and expose kids who cheat at hide-and-seek
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: My shirt is completely stiff and covered in white frost
    lines because I spent seventy-two hours sitting right next to a bulk crate of
    frozen peas
